<Subtitle>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>1</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>9266</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>17102</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>莉琪在体育馆里蹦蹦跳跳。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>2</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>17102</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>20940</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>她假装自己是宠物青蛙呱呱。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>3</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>20940</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>24658</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“呱、呱。” 她叫着。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>4</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>24658</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>27947</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>这是学期结束的前一天。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>5</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>27947</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>36041</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>也意味着这是儿童中心结束的前一天。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>6</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>36041</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>43213</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“请注意，青蛙和赛车手们。” 雪莉老师叫道，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>7</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>43213</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>51752</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我们要做今天的手工——纸花了。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>8</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>51752</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>56145</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>波比从口袋里拿出一张脏纸巾。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>9</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>56145</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>63638</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我这里有一张纸！我刚刚用它擦过鼻涕。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>10</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>63638</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>69427</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“不是那种纸，波比。” 雪莉老师说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>11</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>69427</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>76468</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我们要用干净的包装纸。” 她指着桌子上的彩纸说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>12</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>76468</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>81211</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“呱。我是说，好的。” 莉琪说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>13</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>81211</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>85289</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>尼娜咯咯笑。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>14</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>85289</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>90877</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你们今天真淘气。” 雪莉老师摇摇头说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>15</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>90877</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>93721</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“好了，我们来做花吧。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>16</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>93721</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>101096</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>首先，在纸张的一边折三厘米。然后翻过来。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>17</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>101096</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>105779</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“接下来在同一边再折三厘米。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>18</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>105779</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>114214</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>然后翻过来再折。一直把整张纸折完。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>19</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>114214</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>122081</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“现在把扭扭棒的一端绑在纸张中间。” 雪莉老师说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>20</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>122081</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>126487</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“然后小心地把纸张打开……</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>21</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>126487</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>131514</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>这样就变成一朵好看的花了！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>22</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>131514</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>135390</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“真简单。” 莉琪说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>23</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>135390</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>138710</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>她在做一朵绿色的花。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>24</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>138710</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>145122</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我要再做一个！” 莉琪拿了另一张纸。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>25</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>145122</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>153126</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“进攻！” 波比一边大喊，一边用纸花拍打贾森。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>26</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>153126</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>158540</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“喂！” 贾森拿起花，打了回去。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>27</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>158540</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>165197</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“男生们，这是花，不是剑。” 雪莉老师严厉地说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>28</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>165197</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>168996</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“雪莉老师，您能帮我一下吗？</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>29</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>168996</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>172355</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>我的纸打不开。” 尼娜说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>30</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>172355</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>175402</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>雪莉老师教尼娜怎么做。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>31</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>175402</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>178246</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>莉琪又做了三朵花。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>32</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>178246</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>183408</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>她做完以后，把所有的扭扭棒绑在一起。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>33</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>183408</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>189885</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>然后，她又做了四朵花，把它们也绑在一起。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>34</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>189885</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>197213</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“看！” 莉琪喊，“我是青蛙公主。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>35</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>197213</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>201492</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>她戴着用绿色花做成的王冠。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>36</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>201492</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>205380</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你是我的青蛙王子！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>37</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>205380</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>212693</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>她把另外一个王冠戴在贾森的头上。“呱！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>38</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>212693</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>216107</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>贾森追着莉琪跑。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>39</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>216107</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>220908</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我才不是你的青蛙王子呢！” 他大喊。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>40</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>220908</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>229656</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“哦，贾森和莉琪，天天在一起。” 波比开始唱道。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>41</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>229656</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>232429</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>雪莉老师站起来。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>42</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>232429</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>237148</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“莉琪、贾森、波比，怎么回事？”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>43</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>237148</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>243101</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>莉琪和贾森停了下来。波比也安静下来。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>44</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>243101</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>245765</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他们看着雪莉老师。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>45</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>245765</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>250101</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我本来要带你们去外面， 给你们一份小礼物。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>46</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>250101</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>255515</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>但现在，你们觉得还有资格拿礼物吗？” 雪莉老师说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>47</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>255515</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>257320</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>她很严肃。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>48</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>257320</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>260956</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我在想呱呱。” 莉琪说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>49</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>260956</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>267433</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我想如果呱呱变成青蛙王子，我变成公主会怎么样。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>50</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>267433</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>273597</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>所以我把贾森变成了青蛙王子。对不起。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>51</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>273597</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>277365</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>雪莉老师叹了口气。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>52</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>277365</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>282425</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“好吧。我们整理一下出去吧。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>53</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>282425</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>288465</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>快要出去的时候，莉琪拍了拍老师的手臂。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>54</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>288465</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>292832</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“给您。” 莉琪送给老师一束纸花，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>55</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>292832</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>296996</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“这是我们为您准备的礼物。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>56</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>296996</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>300387</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“呱！” 雪莉老师说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>57</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>300387</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>310114</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“哦不对，谢谢你，青蛙公主！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
</Subtitle>